Boy Confirmation Dusty Blue Faux Silver Religious Invitation

Hot Deals! Boy Confirmation Dusty Blue Faux Silver Religious Invitation – Confirmation Invitations Boy Confirmation Dusty Blue Faux Silver Religious Invitation Have a promotion during this period Boy Confirmation Dusty Blue Faux Silver Religious Invitation quality productsThis elegant dusty blue and silver first communion invitation with a vintage air, recommended for a boy, has an ornate faux silver foil frame with elegant baroque silvery gray decorations on a dusty blue background. Above the text there is a religious cross in faux silver foil. Except the occasion "First Holy Communion", that is also in faux silver, all text can be personalized and has a silvery gray color similar to the faux silver frame.

The vintage, ornate faux silver frame is based on an antique French book cover binding, by Georges Mercier (1885-1939) – Madame de Maupin by Theophile Gautier, edition 1911, now in the public domain. Price:$2.00
